<b>Alma:</b> "Why do you want to bring him back?"
<b>Jonah:</b> "..."
<b>Jonah:</b> "I want to ask for his forgiveness."
<b>Narration:</b> Jonah's voice is quiet as he speaks, soft even.
<b>Narration:</b> Sounds like he's talking more to himself than to me.
<b>Narration:</b> I don't want to push him...

